data.description:
This historic home has all the charm and character you're looking for!! Built in 1901 and structurally renovated in 1985 it's definitely built to last a lifetime. This home is located on 1/4 acre corner lot with room to grow. The first floor boasts beautiful hardwood floors, dark wood ceiling beams and volume ceilings. Double sided wood burning fireplace in the living room and dining room (currently chimney is capped). Bedrooms are trimmed with chair rail and picture frame moldings as well as wood floors. Another wood burning fireplace is located in the bonus room! This home has so many options along with den or study, lots of flexible space here. This is not your cookie cutter run of the mill home, it has many unique touches.




Remarks* - Historic 3/2 home with huge bonus room which has fireplace or could be used as extra large family room/playroom. Den which could be 4th bedroom. fireplaces. Formal dining and living rooms. Master bedroom downstairs. Wood flooring, bamboo flooring in kitchen. Enclosed patio.
data.whatILove: I love that I'm 20 minutes away from just about anything I want to do. Dining, shopping, the springs!! My community is also quite and my neighbors are great.
